title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - Lynchburg
description:
In this video we will have a look at Lynchburg (Virginia) which received a photogrammetry update as part of World Update X which was released already 2 weeks ago. We will depart from Lynchburg regional airport which is at the border of the city and fly multiple times over the city and see if we can recognize some spots.
